{"tid":836294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"取票櫃位不足排長龍　市民哭訴花三小時仍無法購票","createTime":"2018-09-25T14:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T16:12:19.000Z","uid":54627,"like":48,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"231a9efc6d80e565822af59917d8180cce0f66ae","tid":836294,"uid":54627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/220855_8569f7081d7fe590497187eb245a2c5d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F220855_8569f7081d7fe590497187eb245a2c5d.gif&h=300e23da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣深港高鐵香港段已正式開通，今日（25日）仍有不少內地旅客湧至西九龍站取車票，港鐵即使已在站內加開櫃位，但未能足以應付需求。市民程小姐向《香港01》哭訴，已預早兩小時到西九龍站購票，但站內職員指示不清被「亂點」，花上一小時仍未能購票及上車。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵車務總監劉天成早前表示，5個內地段車票櫃枱取票時間較長，故此已要求中國鐵路總公司調配多兩台取票機到西九龍站，現時處理內地車票的櫃位增至7個，相信情況已有改善，亦會研究要否需再加開櫃位。<br />\n<br />\n市民程小姐本打算購買中午12時06分直達貴陽北的車票，她已提前於早上10時到達購票，但現場信息混亂，她指不同的職員指示其到不同的地方，使她到11時30分仍買不到車票。<br />\n<br />\n她指由於需往貴陽掃墓，所以必定要乘搭該班列車，亦怕上不到車而一度情緒激動。及後有港鐵職員前來協助，帶程小姐往購票櫃位的後台。最後，程小姐購得到深圳北轉車至貴陽的車票。<br />\n<br />\n另外，亦有外籍人士因等候取票的時間太長，而未能於開車45分鐘前入閘，他亦一度情緒激動，最後在港鐵職員的協助下，前往購票櫃位，購買另一班列車的車票。"},{"pid":"cfe24a52c5d501934a4ce7cd240b9045a18431a7","tid":836294,"uid":132587,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:11:08.000Z","msg":"番得大陸都係痴痴地線架啦 喊乜柒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3503239c35643c62a013d39af77370501426c79c","tid":836294,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfe24a52c5d501934a4ce7cd240b9045a18431a7","tid":836294,"uid":132587,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:11:08.000Z","msg":"番得大陸都係痴痴地線架啦 喊乜柒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"532f35f8d098bf26c42cb7fc53818a59aa01010e","tid":836294,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:13:04.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"edc261e1eb8e83003fa7ed3c83df6fd474386f0a","tid":836294,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:13:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df14e1deb7508861387096988877e9d28fbb604","tid":836294,"uid":53466,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:14:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a87b7638659b6910334b3c4368c2e216a36c4758","tid":836294,"uid":52595,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:15:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6de98a7e90ff458052a080505bba6fa9a830c1d","tid":836294,"uid":137604,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:15:14.000Z","msg":"膠鐵要跟大陸系統，<br />\n甘就死緊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee0cfe3dc562b650fdace15c32e1757e8d2ac946","tid":836294,"uid":153811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:16:07.000Z","msg":"她只是個孩子!"},{"pid":"481b51ca8bd53066da9720d882f9b67e1e5fd796","tid":836294,"uid":89683,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:16:27.000Z","msg":"唔明點解要咁複雜<br />\n好似坐地鐵咁方便咪好<br />\n<br />\n即買即上幾好"},{"pid":"d069e6bde54d3098d1c798ebdd1a50390a130c88","tid":836294,"uid":145758,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"481b51ca8bd53066da9720d882f9b67e1e5fd796","tid":836294,"uid":89683,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:16:27.000Z","msg":"唔明點解要咁複雜<br />\n好似坐地鐵咁方便咪好<br />\n<br />\n即